songs.title: Baby Bottle Bop Theme Song
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
One, two, three, four!
Baby Bottle Pop, baby bottle pop
You can lick it, shake it, and dunk it
Sweet candy fun!

[Pre-Chorus]
Baby Bottle Pop, baby bottle Pop
You can lick it, shake it and dunk it

[Chorus]
I love it
Gotta have it
Never see me without it my baby
Baby Bottle Pop!

[Chorus]
I love it
Gotta have it
There’s no seeing me without it my baby, yeah
Uh oh, oh!

[Pre-Chorus]
Baby Bottle Pop, baby bottle pop
You can lick it, shake it and dunk it
Sweet candy fun!

[Pre-Chorus]
Baby Bottle Pop, baby Bottle Pop
You can lick it, shake it and dunk it
Uh! Oh! Uh! Oh, oh! Uh oh, oh!

[Outro]
Baby Bottle Pop, baby bottle pop
You can lick it, shake it and dunk it
